sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as Calling Application<br/>(e.g., KFP Component)
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment<br/>Orchestrator
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector<br/>Model Pre-Selection
    participant GAM as GAMOptimizer<br/>HPO Engine
    participant Chunker as LangChainChunker<br/>RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter
    participant OGXEmbed as OGX Embeddings API<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.2+ / API Key
    participant ChromaDB as ChromaDB<br/>In-Memory Vector Store
    participant OGXVec as OGX Vector IO API<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.2+ / API Key
    participant Retriever as Retriever<br/>Similarity Search
    participant OGXChat as OGX Chat API<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.2+ / API Key
    participant Eval as UnitxtEvaluator<br/>Metrics Engine
    participant Handler as EventHandler<br/>(Local / KFP)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Caller,Handler: Flow 1: RAG Optimization Experiment
        Caller->>Exp: run(search_space, benchmark_data)
        Exp->>Handler: on_experiment_start()

        rect rgb(255, 248, 220)
            Note over Exp,Eval: Phase 1: Models Pre-Selection (optional)
            Exp->>MPS: run(model_pairs, sample_data)
            MPS->>OGXEmbed: POST /embeddings<br/>API Key (Bearer)
            OGXEmbed-->>MPS: embedding vectors
            MPS->>ChromaDB: add_documents(chunks)<br/>in-process Python
            MPS->>ChromaDB: similarity_search(query)<br/>in-process Python
            ChromaDB-->>MPS: retrieved contexts
            MPS->>OGXChat: POST /chat/completions<br/>API Key (Bearer)
            OGXChat-->>MPS: generated answers
            MPS->>Eval: evaluate_metrics(predictions, references)
            Eval-->>MPS: scores (faithfulness, correctness)
            MPS-->>Exp: top_model_pairs (pruned)
        end

        rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
            Note over Exp,Eval: Phase 2: Hyperparameter Optimization Loop
            Exp->>GAM: optimize(pruned_search_space)

            loop For each HPO iteration
                GAM->>GAM: select_next_params()<br/>(GAM surrogate prediction)

                GAM->>Chunker: chunk(documents, chunk_size, overlap)
                Chunker-->>GAM: document chunks

                GAM->>OGXEmbed: POST /embeddings<br/>API Key (Bearer)
                OGXEmbed-->>GAM: embedding vectors

                GAM->>OGXVec: POST /vector_stores/{id}/search<br/>API Key (Bearer)
                Note right of OGXVec: Insert chunks &<br/>similarity search
                OGXVec-->>GAM: retrieved contexts

                GAM->>OGXChat: POST /chat/completions<br/>API Key (Bearer)
                Note right of OGXChat: RAG answer generation<br/>(ThreadPoolExecutor, 10 threads)
                OGXChat-->>GAM: generated answers

                GAM->>Eval: evaluate_metrics(predictions, references)
                Eval-->>GAM: scores per question

                GAM->>Handler: on_pattern_creation(PatternPayload)
                GAM->>GAM: fit_gam(results)<br/>update surrogate model
            end

            GAM-->>Exp: best_pattern, all_results
        end

        Exp->>Handler: on_experiment_end(results)
        Exp-->>Caller: ExperimentResults
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over Caller,Handler: Flow 2: Single RAG Pattern Evaluation (Detail)
        Caller->>Exp: run_single_evaluation(params)
        Exp->>Chunker: chunk(documents)
        Chunker-->>Exp: chunks[]
        Exp->>OGXEmbed: embed(chunks)<br/>HTTPS / API Key
        OGXEmbed-->>Exp: vectors[]
        Exp->>OGXVec: add_documents(vectors)<br/>HTTPS / API Key
        OGXVec-->>Exp: indexed
        Exp->>Retriever: retrieve(queries)<br/>HTTPS / API Key
        Retriever->>OGXVec: similarity_search()
        OGXVec-->>Retriever: contexts[]
        Retriever-->>Exp: contexts[]
        Exp->>OGXChat: generate(questions, contexts)<br/>HTTPS / API Key<br/>parallel via ThreadPoolExecutor
        OGXChat-->>Exp: answers[]
        Exp->>Eval: evaluate_metrics()
        Eval-->>Exp: scores{}
        Exp->>Handler: on_pattern_creation(PatternPayload v1.0)
        Exp-->>Caller: pattern_result
    end
